      "created_at": "2022-12-06T01:34:40.053Z",
      "cooked": "<p>I\u2019ve had issues w/ my HR strap/monitor prev (magene H64) where it would freeze sometime and not go up/down. This is a connection issue w/ the Magene and it\u2019s battery I think.</p>\n<p>In your case, you mentioned that the signal only drops on TD App? but you were able to record it properly (w/o issues) on another device and merge it afterwards? Is that correct? If this is true, then likely not an issue w/ the device.</p>\n<p>Just wanted to confirm.</p>",
